#. Tag: title
#: splitter.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>File Splitter</title>"
msgstr "<title>Razdelilnik datotek</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: splitter.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>File Splitter</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Razdelilnik datotek</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function splits one (large) file up into multiple smaller files so that "
"they can be placed on smaller media (&eg; ZIP drives, ...) or sent by email. "
"The multiple files can be combined again to recreate the original file. "
"&krusader; and <trademark class=\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> "
"split/combine functions are compatible. To split a file choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Split</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: a "
"<guilabel>Split</guilabel> dialog will open to confirm the operation."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija razdeli eno (veliko) datoteko na več manjših datotek, tako da "
"jih je mogoče namestiti na manjše medije (&eg; pogone ZIP, ...) ali poslati "
"po e-pošti. Več datotek je mogoče znova združiti, da znova ustvarite izvirno "
"datoteko. &krusader; in funkcije delitve/združevanja <trademark class="
"\"copyright\">Total Commander</trademark> sta združljivi. Če želite datoteko "
"razdeliti, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razdeli</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: odpre se pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Razdeli</guilabel> za potrditev operacije."

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the name of the original file is <filename>foo</filename>, then the name "
"of the smaller files will be <filename>foo.000 foo.001 foo.002</filename> "
"&etc; There is no theoretical limit in the number of smaller files, but it "
"is recommended to limit the number to a maximum of 1023 files. &krusader; "
"creates a <filename>foo.crc</filename> file. This file contains the name, "
"size and the crc checksum of the original file. It is possible to combine "
"the file without the <filename>foo.crc</filename> file but in this case "
"&krusader; cannot check if the original file was recreated correctly."
msgstr ""
"Če je ime izvirne datoteke <filename>foo</filename>, bo ime manjših datotek "
"<filename>foo.000 foo.001 foo.002</filename> &etc; Teoretične omejitve "
"števila manjših datotek ni, vendar je priporočljivo omejiti število na "
"največ 1023 datotek. &krusader; ustvari datoteko <filename>foo.crc</"
"filename>. Ta datoteka vsebuje ime, velikost in kontrolno vsoto crc izvirne "
"datoteke. Datoteko je mogoče združiti brez datoteke <filename>foo.crc</"
"filename>, vendar v tem primeru &krusader; ne more preveriti, ali je bila "
"izvirna datoteka pravilno ponovno ustvarjena."

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "An example of a <filename>foo.crc</filename> file:"
msgstr "Primer datoteke <filename>foo.crc</filename>:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: splitter.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "filename=foo size=432998467868 crc32=21EB719A"
msgstr "filename=foo size=432998467868 crc32=21EB719A"

#. Tag: para
#: splitter.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To combine the multiple files choose, select a partial file <filename>foo."
"xxx</filename> and choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Combine files...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>. The target folder is "
"the inactive panel and can be changed. The file names must be numbered in "
"ascending order: <filename>foo.001, foo.002, foo.003</filename> &etc; or "
"have letters in ascending order: (\" <userinput> <command>split</command> "
"<option>-b</option> </userinput>letter method\") <filename>fileaa, fileab, "
"fileac</filename> &etc; If the file <filename>foo.crc</filename> is found in "
"the same folder as the partial files, &krusader; will use this file to check "
"the combined file for errors."
msgstr ""
"Če želite združiti več izbranih datotek, izberite delno datoteko "
"<filename>foo.xxx</filename> in izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Združi datoteke ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</keycap></keycombo>. Ciljna mapa "
"je neaktivna plošča in jo je mogoče spremeniti. Imena datotek morajo biti "
"oštevilčena v naraščajočem vrstnem redu: <filename>foo.001, foo.002, "
"foo.003</filename> &etc; ali imajo črke v naraščajočem vrstnem redu: (\" "
"<userinput> <command>split</command> <option>-b</option> </userinput>metoda "
"črk\") <filename>fileaa, fileab, fileac</filename> &etc; Če je datoteka "
"<filename>foo.crc</filename> najdena v isti mapi kot delne datoteke, "
"&krusader; bo to datoteko uporabil za preverjanje napak v združeni datoteki."
